 Shearson         -1.7   17.0   51.4    65     30     5
 Smith Barney     -1.5   16.5   47.3    45     35    20
 Goldman Sachs    -2.1   15.1   47.5    35     35    30
 Dean Witter      -2.7   14.4   47.8    85     15     0
