<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
</IN>
<LP>
   BOSTON -- Eastern Utilities Associates said it extended
its tender offers for Fitchburg Gas &amp; Electric Light Co. and
Unitil Corp. from yesterday until midnight Sept. 7, 1990, in
order to give the Securities and Exchange Commission
additional time to review the proposed acquisitions.
   EUA has offered $36 a share for the common stock of
Fitchburg and $40 a share for the common stock of Unitil.
</LP>
