</CO>
<LP>
   OTTAWA -- Canadian bankruptcies rose to 4,104 in March, up
34.9% from 3,043 a year earlier, the federal Consumer and
Corporate Affairs Department said.
   Individual bankruptcies totaled 3,235 and business
bankruptcies totaled 869 in March.
</LP>
